09/09/2003
SOFIA, Bulgaria -- Defence Minister Nikolay Svinarov signed a defence co-operation agreement Monday (8 September) with his Chinese counterpart, Cao Gangchuan.
Svinarov, who is on a visit to China, says both agreed that bilateral relations had made significant progress and should be further strengthened.
Under the agreement, the two ministries would exchange experiences in reforming and modernising their armed forces.
(Xinhua news agency, BTA - 08/09/03)
